TopicTitle: I have a calc test tomorrow :S

Articles.Content:
I scared :-X

I mean, there doesn\'t seem much to know.

But our TA said her exams were easier than anything the professor wanted us to know.

But even so, there isn\'t much material in calculus so far.

I\'m praying to Venus to watch over and guide me while I take my test since it should be directly over-head as I take the test

Good luck, but you could give it a shot and tell this to your teacher:

'I don\'t need to take this test, I have done rocket science and landed on the mun!'
